        <release version="1.4.0" date="2025-01-26">
            <description>
                <p><em>🚀 New Features</em></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Turn pages with mouse wheel</li>
                    <li>Custom name in image saving function</li>
                    <li>Option to save bookmarked images</li>
                    <li>Improved opening behavior options for files and folders</li>
                    <li>Make the Ignore single folders option work for images too</li>
                    <li>Scroll by screen percentage in webtoon mode</li>
                    <li>Shortcuts for saving images</li>
                    <li>Personalize save images template and save automatically to custom folder</li>
                    <li>Multiple poster/folder sizes</li>
                    <li>Implement header scrolling functionality</li>
                    <li>Clear cache for individual files</li>
                    <li>Add support in server settings for show in library the files in subfolders</li>
                    <li>Option to show only one page at a time in Vertical Reader</li>
                    <li>Show files that have lost access on macOS (Store)</li>
                </ul>
                <p><em>🐛 Bug Fixes</em></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Save image not saving the correct page in manga mode</li>
                    <li>Sometimes right click on reading fails</li>
                    <li>Avoid generating thumbnails of images that are still being extracted (Extractions with 7-Zip)</li>
                    <li>Error attempting to open the bookmarks menu after navigating to a bookmark</li>
                    <li>Can't override font in some epub files</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.3.1" date="2024-10-05">
